><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"h-16 flex items-center md:grid md:grid-cols-3 md:gap-4\"><a class=\"flex items-center space-x-2 group\" href=\"/\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-pink-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center\"><span class=\"text-white font-bold text-sm\">MB</span></div><span class=\"font-bold text-xl text-gray-900 group-hover:text-purple-600 transition-colors\">MyBeing</span></a><div class=\"hidden md:flex items-center justify-center gap-8\"><a class=\"relative text-sm font-medium transition-colors hover:text-purple-600 text-gray-700\" href=\"/\">Home</a><a class=\"relative text-sm font-medium transition-colors hover:text-purple-600 text-purple-600\" href=\"/blog\">Articles<div class=\"absolute -bottom-1 left-0 right-0 h-0.5 bg-purple-600 rounded-full\"></div></a><a class=\"relative text-sm font-medium transition-colors hover:text-purple-600 text-gray-700\" href=\"/quizzes\">Quizzes</a><a class=\"relative text-sm font-medium transition-colors hover:text-purple-600 text-gray-700\" href=\"/research\">Research</a><a class=\"relative text-sm font-medium transition-colors hover:text-purple-600 text-gray-700\" href=\"/about\">About</a></div><div class=\"hidden md:flex items-center justify-end gap-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center space-x-3\"><a href=\"/login\"><button class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center font-medium transition-all duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:opacity-50 disabled:pointer-events-none relative overflow-hidden group hover:bg-primary/10 active:scale-[0.98] h-9 px-4 text-sm rounded-lg text-gray-700 hover:text-purple-600\"><span class=\"opacity-100 transition-opacity\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"