reers\">Careers</a></li><li><a class=\"text-gray-300 hover:text-purple-300 text-sm transition-colors\" href=\"/press\">Press</a></li></ul></div><div><h4 class=\"font-semibold text-white mb-6 text-lg\">Support</h4><ul class=\"space-y-3\"><li><a class=\"text-gray-300 hover:text-purple-300 text-sm transition-colors\" href=\"/help\">Help Center</a></li><li><a class=\"text-gray-300 hover:text-purple-300 text-sm transition-colors\" href=\"/privacy\">Privacy Policy</a></li><li><a class=\"text-gray-300 hover:text-purple-300 text-sm transition-colors\" href=\"/terms\">Terms of Service</a></li><li><a class=\"text-gray-300 hover:text-purple-300 text-sm transition-colors\" href=\"/cookies\">Cookie Policy</a></li></ul></div></div><div class=\"border-t border-white/10 pt-12 mb-12\"><div class=\"max-w-md\"><h4 class=\"font-semibold text-white mb-4 text-lg\">The Weekly Reflection</h4><p class=\"text-gray-300 text-sm mb-4\">Weekly insights: research-backed content and self-discovery tools. No spam.</p><form class=\"flex\"><input type=\"email\" class=\"flex w-full rounded-md border px-3 py-1 text-base shadow-sm transition-colors file:border-0 file:bg-transparent file:text-sm file:font-medium file:text-foreground placeholder:text-muted-foreground focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 disabled:cursor-not-allowed disabled:opacity-50 md:text-sm flex-1 h-11 bg-white/10 border-white/20 text-white placeholder-gray-400 rounded-l-lg rounded-r-none focus-visible:ring-brand-500\" placeholder=\"Enter your email\" required=\"\" aria-label=\"Email address\" value=\"\"/><button class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none relative overflow-hidden group bg-primary text-primary-foreground shadow-sm hover:bg-primary/90 hover:shadow-md active:scale-[0.98] text-base rounded-xl h-11 px-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-purple-600 