0\\\",{\\\"children\\\":\\\"The Result\\\"}],\\\": Jennifer lost 30 pounds not through dieting, but by resolving the cognitive dissonance that was driving her stress eating. Her professional confidence also increased dramatically.\\\"]}],\\\"\\\\n\\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mb-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"strong\\\",\\\"strong-0\\\",{\\\"children\\\":\\\"The Lesson\\\"}],\\\": Sometimes the contradiction isn't about the behavior itself—it's about deeper identity conflicts.\\\"]}],\\\"\\\\n\\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h3\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-xl font-bold mt-6 mb-3\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Story 2: The Environmentally Conscious Consumer\\\"}],\\\"\\\\n\\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mb-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"strong\\\",\\\"strong-0\\\",{\\\"children\\\":\\\"The Person\\\"}],\\\": Marcus, a 42-year-old who deeply cared about climate change but lived a high-consumption lifestyle.\\\"]}],\\\"\\\\n\\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mb-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"strong\\\",\\\"strong-0\\\",{\\\"children\\\":\\\"The Surface Contradiction\\\"}],\\\": He posted about environmental issues on social media but drove a gas-guzzling SUV, took frequent flights, and bought new gadgets constantly.\\\"]}],\\\"\\\\n\\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mb-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"strong\\\",\\\"strong-0\\\",{\\\"children\\\":\\\"The Hidden Dissonance\\\"}],\\\": Marcus's environmental values were in constant conflict with his consumer behavior, creating daily mental stress he didn't fully recognize.\\\"]}],\\\"\\\\n\\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mb-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"strong\\\",\\\"strong-0\\\",{\\\"children\\\":\\\"How His Mind Tricked Him:\\\"}]}],\\\"\\\\